## Aggregation

### Sum Operations

```typescript
const csv = `product,quantity,unit_price
Apple,5,1.50
Banana,3,0.75
Orange,8,2.00
Grape,10,0.50`;

const result = parseCSV(csv);

// Total quantity
const totalQty = result.sum('quantity');
console.log(`Total items: ${totalQty}`); // 26

// Total revenue
const totalRevenue = result.rows.reduce((sum, row) => 
  sum + (row.quantity * row.unit_price), 0
);
console.log(`Total revenue: $${totalRevenue.toFixed(2)}`);

// Sum of large orders only
const largeOrderQty = result
  .filter(row => row.quantity > 5)
  .sum('quantity');
console.log(`Large orders: ${largeOrderQty}`); // 18
